Method Detail

createProperty

public Property createProperty(String propertyTypeId,
                               PropertyValue propertyValue,
                               Collection<Grade> grades)
Creates and returns a Property with the specified PropertyValue and Grades. This method generates an identifier for the Property automatically.

Parameters:
propertyTypeId - A String containing the identifier of the PropertyType for the created Property.
propertyValue - The PropertyValue of the created Property, generated using a PropertyValueFactory.
grades - The Grades of the created Property (generated using a GradeFactory), or null to create a property with no grades.
Returns:
See above.
